      "duration": 2.71,
      "size": 43344,
      "text": "欢迎来到蒙特卡洛方法实验！今天我们要用一种神奇的方法来估算圆周率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monte-carlo",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monte-carlo/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "蒙特卡洛方法是一种利用随机数来解决问题的计算方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monte-carlo",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monte-carlo/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.74,
      "size": 43776,
      "text": "它的名字来自摩纳哥的蒙特卡洛赌场，因为这种方法和赌博一样依赖随机性。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monte-carlo",
      "section_id": "principle",
      "line_id": "principle-1",
      "filename": "principle-principle-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monte-carlo/xiaoxiao/principle-principle-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "想象一个边长为2的正方形，里面画一个半径为1的圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monte-carlo",
      "section_id": "principle",
      "line_id": "principle-2",
      "filename": "principle-principle-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monte-carlo/xiaoxiao/principle-principle-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.39,
      "size": 22176,
      "text": "正方形的面积是4，圆的面积是π。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monte-carlo",
      "section_id": "principle",
      "line_id": "principle-3",
      "filename": "principle-principle-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monte-carlo/xiaoxiao/principle-principle-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.36,
      "size": 53712,
      "text": "如果我们在正方形内随机撒点，落入圆内的概率就是圆面积除以正方形面积，等于π除以4。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monte-carlo",
      "section_id": "principle",
      "line_id": "principle-4",
      "filename": "principle-principle-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monte-carlo/xiaoxiao/principle-principle-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "所以，圆内点数除以总点数，再乘以4，就能估算出π的值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monte-carlo",
      "section_id": "visualization",
